Thank you!  This is awesome.  My wife loves this show.  Makes me a little nervous actually but that's another episode, I mean story...

I noticed a few episodes were out of order.  Also the unknown season episodes come from various seasons including 3, 4, 5, 6, and 7.  The correct numbers can be found on Wikipedia since IMDB, TV.com and TVDB are not accurate either.

There are 9 total seasons, anyone have more of this shit?
